est dispersion\n(0.066 mag). In addition, the average mid-IR extinction curve for Cepheids has\nbeen obtained: A_W1/A_Ks=0.560, A_W2/A_Ks=0.479, A_W3/A_Ks=0.507,\nA_W4/A_Ks=0.406, A_[3.6]/A_Ks=0.481, A_[4.5]/A_Ks=0.469, A_[5.8]/A_Ks=0.427,\nand A_[8.0]/A_Ks=0.427 mag.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Nov 2017 04:29:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Dec 2017 13:22:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
