d quasinormal frequencies can be\nobtained by considering Neumann boundary conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Nov 2017 13:02:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 May 2018 21:07:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
